title.narrative: DEMAND FOR THE USE OF HEALTH SERVICES

description.narrative: By 2020, there is an increased community demand for and use of health services in the vulnerable regions, including in emergency situations, which contributes to Child Health, Immunization, Immunization (Covid), Maternal And Newborn Health. UNICEF aims to achieve this through Advocacy And Public Engagement, Fostering Innovation And Use Of New Technologies, United Nations Working Together. This contributes to the following Country Programme result: Children and women in vulnerable regions have access to and use a package of quality promotional, preventive and curative health interventions, including in emergency situations.
